    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions",
        "authentication": "predefinedCredentialType",
        "nodeCredentialType": "openAiApi",
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"model\": \"gpt-4o\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"system\",\n      \"content\": \"You are a viral TikTok/Instagram video strategist for dropshipping products. Your goal: create UGC-style video scripts that convert.\\n\\nKEY PRINCIPLES (2026):\\n- UGC ads get 3× higher CTR than branded ads\\n- Videos <30 sec get 50% engagement rate\\n- 75%+ completion rate = algorithmic boost\\n- Anti-AI detection: use human imperfections, natural speech\\n- Doomscrolling hooks: guilt redirect, time scarcity\\n\\nOUTPUT FORMAT:\\n{\\n  \\\"strategy\\\": {\\n    \\\"hook_type\\\": \\\"doomscroll_guilt|before_after|problem_solution\\\",\\n    \\\"mood\\\": \\\"energetic|calm|upbeat\\\",\\n    \\\"target_emotion\\\": \\\"FOMO|curiosity|relief\\\"\\n  },\\n  \\\"script\\\": {\\n    \\\"hook\\\": \\\"First 3 seconds text (guilt redirect hook)\\\",\\n    \\\"body\\\": \\\"Main script 15-20 seconds (natural, contractions, filler words)\\\",\\n    \\\"cta\\\": \\\"Call to action 3-5 seconds\\\"\\n  },\\n  \\\"midjourney_prompts\\\": [\\n    \\\"Prompt 1: Opening shot (hook visual)\\\",\\n    \\\"Prompt 2: Problem/Before shot\\\",\\n    \\\"Prompt 3: Product in action\\\",\\n    \\\"Prompt 4: After/Result shot\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"timing\\\": [\\n    {\\\"image\\\": 1, \\\"duration\\\": 3, \\\"text_overlay\\\": \\\"hook text\\\"},\\n    {\\\"image\\\": 2, \\\"duration\\\": 5, \\\"text_overlay\\\": null},\\n    {\\\"image\\\": 3, \\\"duration\\\": 7, \\\"text_overlay\\\": null},\\n    {\\\"image\\\": 4, \\\"duration\\\": 5, \\\"text_overlay\\\": \\\"CTA text\\\"}\\n  ],\\n  \\\"performance_estimate\\\": {\\n    \\\"viral_score\\\": 1-10,\\n    \\\"estimated_ctr\\\": \\\"X-Y%\\\",\\n    \\\"target_completion_rate\\\": \\\"XX%\\\"\\n  }\\n}\\n\\nMIDJOURNEY PROMPT RULES:\\n- Always use: 'shot on iPhone 15 Pro, handheld camera with natural shake'\\n- Include: 'natural window lighting, golden hour sunlight'\\n- Add imperfections: 'slight motion blur, thumb partially visible in corner'\\n- UGC authenticity: 'mild grain, off-center composition, casual home environment'\\n- Format: '--style raw --v 6 --ar 9:16'\\n- AVOID banned words: nude, violence, drugs, etc.\\n\\nSCRIPT RULES:\\n- Use contractions (it's, that's, you're)\\n- Filler words ok: \\\"like\\\", \\\"literally\\\", \\\"okay so\\\"\\n- Natural pauses: *sigh*, *laugh*, em-dashes\\n- Typos in text overlays ok (lowercase, no punctuation)\\n- Address viewer directly: \\\"you\\\", \\\"your\\\"\\n\\nDOOMSCROLL HOOKS (examples):\\n- \\\"you've been scrolling for 10 minutes...\\\"\\n- \\\"POV: you're supposed to be working\\\"\\n- \\\"me pretending I didn't just waste an hour\\\"\\n- \\\"okay but hear me out—\\\"\\n\\nNow generate for the product.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"Product: {{ $json.product_name }}\\n\\nDescription: {{ $json.product_description }}\\n\\nTarget audience: {{ $json.target_audience }}\\n\\nPrice: {{ $json.price }}\\n\\nUnique selling points: {{ $json.unique_selling_points.join(', ') }}\\n\\nGenerate viral TikTok video strategy + script + Midjourney prompts.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"temperature\": 0.9,\n  \"response_format\": { \"type\": \"json_object\" }\n}",
        "options": {}
      },
